OL,3,CTrump says King 'agrees with me' that
OL,4,CIran should never have nuclear weapon
OL,6,FUS President Donald Trump has insisted
OL,7,Fthe King agrees with him that Iran
OL,8,Fshould never be allowed nuclear
OL,9,Fweapons.
OL,11,FThe American leader made the remarks
OL,12,Fat the White House state dinner on
OL,13,FTuesday evening, saying he had
OL,14,F"militarily defeated that particular
OL,15,Fopponent".
OL,17,FMr Trump in his toast at the grand
OL,18,Fevent in honour of Charles and the
OL,19,FQueen said: "We're doing a little
OL,20,FMiddle East work right now, ... and
OL,21,Fwe're doing very well.
OL,26,@vD@AOUwD@IO]{D@MOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/14
