PN,31802
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F318A1777558268
OL,3,CTrump says King 'agrees with me' that
OL,4,CIran should never have nuclear weapon
OL,6,F"We have militarily defeated that
OL,7,Fparticular opponent, and we're never
OL,8,Fgoing to let that opponent ever,
OL,9,FCharles agrees with me even more than
OL,10,FI do, we're never going to let that
OL,11,Fopponent have a nuclear weapon.
OL,13,F"They know that, and they've known it
OL,14,Fright now, very powerfully."
OL,16,FThe remarks risk drawing the monarch
OL,17,Finto the political row over the crisis
OL,18,Fin the Middle East.
OL,26,@nD@AOUuD@AOUvD@\O]
