OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F318A1777558268
OL,3,CTrump says King 'agrees with me' that
OL,4,CIran should never have nuclear weapon
OL,6,FAnd he also quipped about the US's
OL,7,Fspace travel, saying: "Now, I know you
OL,8,Fhave big plans for the Moon, Mr
OL,9,FPresident, but I've actually checked
OL,10,Fthe papers and I rather suspect it is
OL,11,Falready part of the Commonwealth, I'm
OL,12,Fafraid."
OL,26,@oD@WOUtD@HO]
