CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F318A1777558268
OL,3,CTrump says King 'agrees with me' that
OL,4,CIran should never have nuclear weapon
OL,6,FThe Queen was dressed in a deep pink
OL,7,FFiona Clare evening gown, and an
OL,8,Famethyst and diamond necklace which
OL,9,Fbelonged to Queen Victoria's mother
OL,10,Fthe Duchess of Kent, while the King
OL,11,Fand Mr Trump were in white tie and
OL,12,FFirst Lady Melania Trump wore a pale
OL,13,Fsilk off the shoulder Christian Dior
OL,14,Fgown for the special gathering.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G11/14
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
