CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F318A1777558268
OL,3,CTrump says King 'agrees with me' that
OL,4,CIran should never have nuclear weapon
OL,6,FAmong the 120 guests were golfing ace
OL,7,FRory McIlroy, Amazon boss Jeff Bezos
OL,8,Fand his wife Lauren, outgoing Apple
OL,9,Fchief Tim Cook, Eric and Lara Trump,
OL,10,FIvanka Trump and Jared Kushner,
OL,11,FTiffany Trump and Michael Boulos, and
OL,12,Fthe UK's ambassador to the US Sir
OL,13,FChristian Turner.
OL,15,FOthers on the list included US
OL,16,Fsecretary of state Marco Rubio, his UK
OL,17,Fcounterpart Yvette Cooper, US defence
OL,18,Fsecretary Pete Hegseth and General Dan
OL,19,FCaine, chairman of the Joint Chiefs of
OL,20,FStaff.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G12/14
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
