PN,31814
SC,0014
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F318A1777558268
OL,3,CTrump says King 'agrees with me' that
OL,4,CIran should never have nuclear weapon
OL,6,FThe King's earlier address to Congress
OL,7,Fon Capitol Hill saw him become only
OL,8,Fthe second British monarch to do so
OL,9,Fafter his mother Queen Elizabeth II in
OL,10,F1991, and the first British king.
OL,12,FCharles told Congress that the
OL,13,Fpartnership between the two nations is
OL,14,F"more important today than it has ever
OL,15,Fbeen".
OL,26,@vD@AOUwD@EO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G14/14
